# Superpowers subagent-driven-development scratch (machine-generated task briefs/
# reports). A nested .superpowers/sdd/.gitignore already hides these from git, but
# Prettier only reads the root ignore files — declaring the dir here keeps the
# repo-wide `prettier --check .` gate green on these local-only transcripts.
.superpowers/

# Specification authoring work items
.project-pipeline/
